  "title": "Guess How Much I Love You",
  "description": "Welcome the family classic with an elegant, refreshed cover — the quintessential picture book, just waiting to be shared.\r\n\r\nSometimes, when you love someone very, very much, you want to find a way of describing how much you treasure them. But, as Little Nutbrown Hare and Big Nutbrown Hare discover, love is not an easy thing to measure! For two decades, Sam McBratney’s timelessly endearing story, beautifully rendered in Anita Jeram’s exquisite watercolors, has captured the deep and tender bond between parent and child. Guess How Much I Love You is one of the world’s best-loved picture books.",
